  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load all knowledge files including the dispatch-path decision doc from task 001.</step>
    <step order="2">Read existing `AnalysisOrchestrationService` invocation patterns to identify the entry-point signature for a code-level dispatch (Path B); if dispatch decision is Path A, read `sprk_playbookconsumer` service entry-point.</step>
